resources.string: He loves being with his brother squeaky. Both were owner surrender to humane society since owner could not keep because apartment complex would not allow. Escape artist and will look for a way out to run and play! JUMPERS, CAN JUMP HIGH!!
She is very smart! She knows sit and shake and is even crate trained! Arthur loves dogs but is not cat tested. She is a cat who wants to please his humans and is very sweet!!

She is a very shy girl that will need time to come out of her shell. Loud noises while walking do make her nervous so a confident and experienced owner is important. Since She is nervous with new things.
He is a very fun cat that will entertain himself with literally anything. He loves all kinds of toys.
She is a gorgeous girl that is mostly quite unless there is food, and will always demand more when she finishes her plate.
